rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0001
rows.name:
We at Kurolo are discussing how much
Invidia has developed, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Recently, thanks to someone, Invidia
has developed rapidly, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0003
rows.name:
After various analyses, we've found that
shopping isn't the only factor in
development, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0004
rows.name: First, helping people in need, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0005
rows.name:
When a problem is solved, anxiety about
the future disappears... this is one of the factors
in a country's development, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0007
rows.name:
The fact that requests to the mercenary group are
being taken care of means that life is improving
on both an individual and national level, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0008
rows.name: Then, talking to various people, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0009
rows.name:
Surely the active exchange of information and
increased interaction between people is also a
factor, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0011
rows.name:
If someone finds it, many people
will come to know about it, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0012
rows.name:
There might be new resources there, leading
to the country's development, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0013
rows.name:
...And so, it seems that's how a country
develops, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0014
rows.name:
This long talk is tiring, mo...
Please let this be the only time I have to explain it... mo.
